{"tid":446150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集體每日搵唔同部門投訴旺角行人專用區，有無得諗？","createTime":"2017-10-24T05:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T21:54:26.000Z","uid":54046,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e644e6326f5703ee60ef5d9457bdaa9e63445406","tid":446150,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:04:05.000Z","msg":"警察-嘈音，如果有人拎野佈置，可以投訴埋攻擊性武器<br />\n食環-阻街（成唔成立都好，叫左佢黎煩人先）<br />\n環境處-嘈音<br />\n消防-睇下班仆街有無阻到消防設備，有既又可以做<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n要佢地日日煩下佢地都好"},{"pid":"b7d1cbfb294e39cdeb59bec0a7d29755d303565b","tid":446150,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"班大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210de7b780e3e966af05656aff521b198620a69d","tid":446150,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"你要同投訴部門講你企晌現場等到佢嚟先會真係有人嚟處理, 其實成本唔低架."},{"pid":"e036f5ee31e0b60d57ddebb81e1e58ac02ebf6cd","tid":446150,"uid":75556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要同投訴部門講你企晌現場等到佢嚟先會真係有人嚟處理, 其實成本唔低架.</blockquote><br />\n咪輪流叫定先lo，有人見到叫定再到場"},{"pid":"2c4fdf8f59af783d95b18bccaa0bc536cfc5b024","tid":446150,"uid":57584,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T09:54:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce663804905d1d59f583a8adb4674b7b5fa11eba","tid":446150,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T21:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49e8b9f1daeb592a393a0bbec169680901c7a75","tid":446150,"uid":48011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T21:35:27.000Z","msg":"我可以同你講冇用 <br />\n利申住附近"},{"pid":"3f92fa3f6dd2b2cb143f5088bdfebdd4e1c737e3","tid":446150,"uid":47359,